OL,3,CPlans for legislation to allow
OL,4,Crecording and broadcasting in certain
OL,5,Ccourtrooms
OL,7,FJustice Minister Naomi Long has
OL,8,Fconfirmed that she is to move forward
OL,9,Fwith plans to allow news outlets to
OL,10,Fsend cameras into Crown and Appeal
OL,11,Fcourts to record and broadcast
OL,12,Fsentencing remarks by judges.
OL,14,FThe move, which follows a public
OL,15,Fconsultation, will bring Northern
OL,16,FIreland in line with the rest of the
OL,17,FUnited Kingdom.
