OL,3,CPlans for legislation to allow
OL,4,Crecording and broadcasting in certain
OL,5,Ccourtrooms
OL,7,FHowever, the Department of Justice has
OL,8,Fsaid that new legislation will have to
OL,9,Fbe drawn up and this will be deferred
OL,10,Funtil after the next Assembly
OL,11,Felections.
OL,13,FMs Long's department is set to work
OL,14,Fclosely with the Office of the Lady
OL,15,FChief Justice Dame Siobhan Keegan in
OL,16,Fdeveloping the plans.
OL,18,FMs Long said broadcasting in courts
OL,19,Fwill increase transparency in terms of
OL,20,Fthe justice system.
