OL,5,Ccourtrooms
OL,7,F"Allowing broadcasting in courts will
OL,8,Fincrease transparency and allow the
OL,9,Fpublic to view decisions being made by
OL,10,Fthe judiciary in Northern Ireland,"
OL,11,Fshe said.
OL,13,F"This can only be a good thing,
OL,14,Fhowever, I am aware some respondents
OL,15,Fto the public consultation did express
OL,16,Fconcerns about the impact of the
OL,17,Fproposals on victims and children.
