OL,5,Ccourtrooms
OL,7,F"It's important to stress the
OL,8,Fbroadcasting of certain court
OL,9,Fproceedings will, in essence, simply
OL,10,Fprovide another way for journalists to
OL,11,Fcover proceedings on which they can
OL,12,Falready report.
OL,14,F"Members of the public, including
OL,15,Fvictims, witnesses and jurors, will
OL,16,Fnot be filmed or recorded.
