OL,3,CPlans for legislation to allow
OL,4,Crecording and broadcasting in certain
OL,5,Ccourtrooms
OL,7,F"Furthermore, the decision on whether
OL,8,Fa case can be recorded or broadcast
OL,9,Fwill lie with the individual judge,
OL,10,Fand any reporting restrictions will
OL,11,Fcontinue to apply regardless of how
OL,12,Fproceedings are reported upon."
OL,14,FMs Long added: "This is not about
OL,15,Fturning our courts into livestream
OL,16,Fentertainment; it is about improving
OL,17,Fpublic confidence in our justice
OL,18,Fsystem and, as always, victims and
OL,19,Fwitnesses will remain at the heart of
OL,20,Feverything we do."
